description:
Thank you so much to Esje from the Banshee Labyrinth for putting together this awesome story for us.


Thank you also to the Banshee Labyrinth and The Edinburgh Horror Festival for offering us the opportunity to do our first live show.


We're sad that it wasn't to be this year but also so delighted that we even had the chance to be a part of it!

If you're interested - please have a look at the Ed Horror Fest website to see if there is any online show that catches your eye:


https://www.edhorrorfest.co.uk/


While you're at it, check out the Banshee Labyrinth:


https://www.thebansheelabyrinth.com


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
